{"tid":2326173,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"渣打料本港失業率或明年上半年見頂達7%","createTime":"2020-12-15T06:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:18:07.000Z","uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"101be3083e453c2ba4caa7dee4c71915a1581b03","tid":2326173,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"渣打料本港失業率或明年上半年見頂達7% <br />\n<br />\n財經 發佈時間 15.12.2020 12:53 最後更新時間 15.12.2020 12:53 <br />\n<br />\n渣打香港大中華區高級經濟師劉健恒表示，雖然今季出現新一輪疫情，亦有收緊措施，但收緊措施較遲才出現，基於第三季經濟有改善，預期本港第四季GDP按季有增長，按年收縮1.8%，渣打維持對本港今年經濟收縮5.8%的預測，並預期明年經濟增長4%。 他認為，本港未來一年復蘇會較淺，主要受惠於外部環境利好因素所支持，包括寬鬆貨幣政策及低息環境，而負面因素較多來自內部因素。他又預計，失業率最快明年上半年才見頂，屆時或升至7%，又認為政府有需要亦有能力推出第四輪支持經濟措施，規模雖不及之前大，預料新一財年赤字相當於GDP達4.5%亦難以避免。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2370725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Ffinance%2F2370725&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=75ba9861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/finance/2370725</a>"},{"pid":"f706f632af6d5a436242af81332671b2240bc4b1","tid":2326173,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">咁樂觀呀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0837864767dc5e86ff8c1d296081481d5fc664f9","tid":2326173,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"唔係破十咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353ee8398ef01e1bfd5500095ee263788de56d68","tid":2326173,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"正常 7% 唔多 ,  樓市仲好穩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010051ea3f1ffa318555bbb63d4599f25a32c54e","tid":2326173,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike